data.description: Stunning corner lot nestled in the Palisades at Country Place! Step inside and you are greeted with natural lighting, open flowing layout with soothing color tones and great entertaining space. The kitchen is equip with stainless steel appliances, dual sink and plant shelving. Generously sized bedrooms with modern bathroom vanities. Private master suite with steps to a separate loft area.
